  \<Longrightarrow> lzip (lappend xs ys) (lappend us vs) = lappend (lzip xs us) (lzip ys vs)"
by(coinduction arbitrary: xs ys us vs rule: llist.strong_coinduct)(auto 4 6 simp add: llength_ltl)

lemma llength_lzip [simp]:
